{"tid":1786740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【1224平安夜】和你shop，尖沙咀大遊行點解無人知，連日程表都無，說好的聖誕攬炒呢","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T06:54:39.000Z","uid":320676,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"5afd2012582e56cf5ccd2a1aa62aa92f953cace6","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.多區願平安歸香港 行動</span><br />\n平安夜就緊係出街shopping，無論你係毒撚、和理非、藍絲都可以一齊去呢10個商場shopping，一定有好多人陪你<br />\nChannel:<a href=\"https://t.me/xmasevehkchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehkchannel&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=c3a28f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/xmasevehkchannel</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udv7s2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fudv7s2N.jpg&h=1eb0a5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mA48cut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmA48cut.jpg&h=23fa0225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuXd72O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuXd72O.jpg&h=7541d8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EecNs2P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEecNs2P.jpg&h=1015ed11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kn6Kvga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKn6Kvga.jpg&h=7e431af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.尖沙嘴大遊行</span><br />\n平安夜天氣寒冷，為咗要取暖，大家可以出去尖沙咀圍爐，大家儘量出<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAjss4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAjss4f.jpg&h=d6800e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">副本</span><br />\n當日黨鐵有延長到凌晨嘅服務，大家記得要跳閘，捐閘，踢閘，跳欄，用老人卡，組隊跳閘。<br />\n1個人跳閘自己好危險，100萬人跳閘黨鐵就好危險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你平安夜果日有咩事，夜晚都要出嚟，一係和你shop，一係尖沙咀，點都要出一個。咩嘢和理非怕危險，要點樣點樣，唔想中計等等，全部都唔係籍口。出嚟啊香港人，出去啊屌你老母，<br />\n出嚟呀出嚟呀出嚟呀"},{"pid":"4e3bf8c7ee9be6dff743092bb1aeb42d6baeb0cc","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"1/100"},{"pid":"a2a91f576eba34416bc0cf826962e43f2253f128","tid":1786740,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3e26147b2d442d6da38ff91285a9f0d397442b88","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"2/100"},{"pid":"4bf514f4cfa0556f624a7066ad1830de75fc3f25","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"3/100"},{"pid":"d58ec477277651dc8f139877b422d9f0caf31985","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"4/100"},{"pid":"865ac04a268ab5a2d3a231e2dc9c6c6dfe3ffe12","tid":1786740,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c39e42d77774a11df6ab95a3d9f96c475ea0589","tid":1786740,"uid":158105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"大力推！"},{"pid":"9034b6a0fbf16e71217cc4a5c6d3c250178d18dc","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"5/100"},{"pid":"6976b8f058f88e6d2f71ae876eaf51d49a152a97","tid":1786740,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"6/100"},{"pid":"ef56bc5bfb7